{"tid":2137750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警：「李力持」本人的專頁涉嫌教唆他人偽造記者證  因證據不足不會檢控","createTime":"2020-08-03T07:15:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T11:14:19.000Z","uid":22556,"like":4,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f33de68502cd31eed7737246c10f89b6c7d8b35e","tid":2137750,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T07:15:41.000Z","msg":"香港記者協會今年5月16日主動報案，舉報有人在名為「李力持」的Facebook專頁，上載本會記者證樣本，並留言「邊位想做記者可以自己DIY」，涉嫌教唆他人偽造本會記者證。經兩個多月後，本會接獲警方來信，表示認為證據不足以支持對任何人作出起訴，因此不會採取檢控行動。<br />\n<br />\n記協正研究跟進行動，並會向警方查詢調查詳情，包括證據如何不足及是否已結案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/242729300308/posts/10158435517985309/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F242729300308%2Fposts%2F10158435517985309%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2F51QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=f9c02914\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/242729300308/posts/10158435517985309/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"d85395f45a5c3fa8e812483155927d87516b4b4f","tid":2137750,"uid":42188,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T07:17:20.000Z","msg":"我睇唔到 我唔知道"},{"pid":"303dc4bb43341d2d2081d56ccda2f16f7f6d8aeb","tid":2137750,"uid":97080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T07:19:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccf82a30c01b7f93e874a67eb8c34d5b60421be2","tid":2137750,"uid":26014,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T07:19:52.000Z","msg":"有證據又話證據不足，手足身上冇鐳射筆都要坐，然後警察話自己嚴正執法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc293530fae29d055a32aa57a432d7ebc1f3249b","tid":2137750,"uid":19213,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f33de68502cd31eed7737246c10f89b6c7d8b35e","tid":2137750,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T07:15:41.000Z","msg":"香港記者協會今年5月16日主動報案，舉報有人在名為「李力持」的Facebook專頁，上載本會記者證樣本，並留言「邊位想做記者可以自己DIY」，涉嫌教唆他人偽造本